tspan.tspan: Multi-Channel Analyzers sort pseudo-gaussian input pulses into channels based on their peak height in order to
generate a spectrum. Our compact, USB-powered MCA devices and accompanying cross-platform data acquisition
software enables easy visualization and analysis of pulse outputs from shaping amplifiers.
